						<div class="postbody">The 2C03 and 2C05 are garish versions of the 2C02 palette ... just missing two extra greys.<br /><br />It appears that the 2C04 took advantage of the cheapo DRM scrambling the 2C03's palette to add another 10 colors to address a few shortcomings.</div>

